{"tid":46134,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"香港係咪有咁多純情女呀","createTime":"2016-12-19T12:38:05.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-19T15:38:43.000Z","uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"21127cf4d046613e4e8de1f00fb38d4231efdc4c","tid":46134,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T12:38:05.000Z","msg":"受害女事主廿六歲，據悉，她因工作關係社交圈子狹窄，早前在社交媒體Facebook結識一名男網友，由於兩人志趣相投，漸交往頻密，對方更刻意扮成「老實人」，在網上與事主誠摯交談，愈談愈覺投契，在甜言蜜語下漸墮網戀。期間，男方不斷相約她見面，初時事主仍有戒心，惟心軟終於答應。<br />\n<br />\n日前她獨自前往屯門應約，<span style=\"color: red;\">眼前素未謀面情郎卻是染金髮肥仔</span>，其後，她被誘騙往龍門路一單位內，當時屋內無任何人，事主已忐忑不安欲離開，但被人阻止，更露出猙獰淫相，以霸王硬上弓向她施暴強姦，更將其禁錮。直到前日傍晚六時許，有鄰居聽到該單位傳出淒楚女子呼救聲，恐怕發生意外，遂報警求助。"},{"pid":"e24221a3e3cc2a83584ed2b68ff7e8201190b25b","tid":46134,"uid":9581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T12:42:43.000Z","msg":"小妹好純情"},{"pid":"f9cf1e7afd8228bb842760187769907a43e8e12f","tid":46134,"uid":4492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T12:43:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小妹好純情</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我知吖"},{"pid":"ea5b8ce72043a146d4a1157cc02ab5be3fb224cd","tid":46134,"uid":39080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T12:51:19.000Z","msg":"我仲純情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1503fdd6d76a206928ecd1e3f054cc2a9f26359","tid":46134,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T12:52:09.000Z","msg":"小妹好純情"},{"pid":"ae3269ded531d7b6d7629b838391a552d8fdfa20","tid":46134,"uid":12201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T12:52:41.000Z","msg":"條MK仔有排坐囉今次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8805660973d9f0e5421d0b2f7871f73a2b8eb5db","tid":46134,"uid":10897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T12:56:01.000Z","msg":"樓上班偽娘收檔啦"},{"pid":"c74a4a09ca0cd580c404e91c613f0c5e5938341a","tid":46134,"uid":9581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0